{
  "chapter": 137,
  "chapter_summary": "寇仲与跋锋寒藏身屋内，杜干木率人搜索之际，徐子陵于后院遇王世充甥女董淑妮。董淑妮称越王图谋杀害王世充，自己欲往偃师报信。沈落雁与王伯当率瓦岗军至，商议追捕。跋锋寒现身迎敌，一剑斩杀敌将，纵火制造混乱后脱身。四人在黄河边会合休憩。寇仲从董淑妮口中套出幕后主使乃独孤家，并探知洛阳守将多为王世充心腹。跋锋寒与徐子陵探路归来，众人赶赴偃师。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "小陵似在后面和一个女子说话，究竟是甚么一回事呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 137,
      "line_start": 7,
      "line_end": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ba_feng_han",
      "speaker_name": "跋锋寒",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "只要不是涫妖女又或祝玉妍，我们便不需为他担心吧！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 137,
      "line_start": 11,
      "line_end": 11
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_ba_feng_han",
      "text": "来的说不定是寻找我们的敌人，最好和杜干木等一言不合先打一场，那我们就可坐收渔人之利。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 137,
      "line_start": 17,
      "line_end": 17
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ba_feng_han",
      "speaker_name": "跋锋寒",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "你的愿望该可实现哩！因为来的是瓦岗军。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 137,
      "line_start": 21,
      "line_end": 23
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dong_shu_ni",
      "speaker_name": "董淑妮",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "你知人家是谁！你却尚未说出自己的名字呢？",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 137,
      "line_start": 27,
      "line_end": 29
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_dong_shu_ni",
      "text": "我叫徐子陵！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 137,
      "line_start": 31,
      "line_end": 31
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dong_shu_ni",
      "speaker_name": "董淑妮",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "我听很多人提过你们，说你和寇仲是年青一辈中最有潜质的其中两个人，那在外面的当然有个是寇仲了。嘻！幸好我躲到这里来，你们定要负起保护人家的责任啊！",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 137,
      "line_start": 35,
      "line_end": 39
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_dong_shu_ni",
      "text": "你若想我们保护你，首先要告诉我们究竟是谁要伤害你？而你又为何一个人逃到这里来？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 137,
      "line_start": 43,
      "line_end": 45
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dong_shu_ni",
      "speaker_name": "董淑妮",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "他们是越王的人，越王要杀我大舅舅，给奴家知道了，越王便派人来追杀我，淑妮于是坐船逃走，岂知给追兵赶上。嘻！幸好奴家的轻功不错，于是溜到了这里来，又幸好遇上你们。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 137,
      "line_start": 47,
      "line_end": 51
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_dong_shu_ni",
      "text": "越王为何要杀你大舅舅？他不是个只十多岁的小孩子吗？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 137,
      "line_start": 53,
      "line_end": 53
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dong_shu_ni",
      "speaker_name": "董淑妮",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "功高震主兼奸人唆使，从古以来都是这样子的嘛。奴家现在要赶到偃师去见大舅舅，你们肯送奴家去吗？另外那个不像汉人的好看男子又是谁呢？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 137,
      "line_start": 57,
      "line_end": 61
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ba_feng_han",
      "speaker_name": "跋锋寒",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "情况有点不对头，先听听他们有甚么话说。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 137,
      "line_start": 67,
      "line_end": 69
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_gan_mu",
      "speaker_name": "杜干木",
      "listener": "char_shen_luo_yan",
      "text": "我们已依从沈军师的指示，从大河那边搜过来，仍发现不到她的踪影。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 137,
      "line_start": 71,
      "line_end": 73
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_luo_yan",
      "speaker_name": "沈落雁",
      "listener": "char_du_gan_mu",
      "text": "杜将军请放心，我们已在周围五十里内布下天罗地网，任她轻功如何高明，也是插翼难飞。但要注意会有高手为她护驾，否则我的鸟儿就不会伤了左翼。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 137,
      "line_start": 81,
      "line_end": 85
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_bo_dang",
      "speaker_name": "王伯当",
      "listener": "char_shen_luo_yan",
      "text": "这么机密的事，为何会让那个只懂迷惑男人的董淑妮知悉呢？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 137,
      "line_start": 89,
      "line_end": 91
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_gan_mu",
      "speaker_name": "杜干木",
      "listener": "char_shen_luo_yan",
      "text": "正是朝中有人迷恋她的美色，想藉此讨她欢心，致泄了机密，幸好给我们及时发觉，现在只要把她抓起来，亡羊补牢，尚未为晚也。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 137,
      "line_start": 95,
      "line_end": 97
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ba_feng_han",
      "speaker_name": "跋锋寒",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "如此机密之事，各位竟在光天化日下当街谈论，实是儿戏之极，可笑啊可笑！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 137,
      "line_start": 115,
      "line_end": 117
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_gan_mu",
      "speaker_name": "杜干木",
      "listener": "char_ba_feng_han",
      "text": "跋锋寒！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 137,
      "line_start": 119,
      "line_end": 119
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_bo_dang",
      "speaker_name": "王伯当",
      "listener": "char_ba_feng_han",
      "text": "这叫天堂有路你不走，地狱无门却闯进来。我们正奉命找你，另两个小子在那里？",
      "tone": "狂笑",
      "chapter": 137,
      "line_start": 121,
      "line_end": 123
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ba_feng_han",
      "speaker_name": "跋锋寒",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我既敢站出来，自然有应付你们的把握。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 137,
      "line_start": 127,
      "line_end": 127
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ba_feng_han",
      "speaker_name": "跋锋寒",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我跋锋寒身经大小千百战，却从未有人能取我之命，且看你们能否捡得例外甜头。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 137,
      "line_start": 149,
      "line_end": 151
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_luo_yan",
      "speaker_name": "沈落雁",
      "listener": "char_ba_feng_han",
      "text": "寇仲和徐子陵究竟到哪里去了？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 137,
      "line_start": 157,
      "line_end": 157
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ba_feng_han",
      "speaker_name": "跋锋寒",
      "listener": "char_shen_luo_yan",
      "text": "我负责杀人，他们负责放火，这样说沈军师清楚了吧？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 137,
      "line_start": 159,
      "line_end": 161
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_luo_yan",
      "speaker_name": "沈落雁",
      "listener": "char_ba_feng_han",
      "text": "不好！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 137,
      "line_start": 163,
      "line_end": 163
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ba_feng_han",
      "speaker_name": "跋锋寒",
      "listener": "char_shen_luo_yan",
      "text": "太迟了！",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 137,
      "line_start": 165,
      "line_end": 165
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我的天，终于到了，娘！这就是大河！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 137,
      "line_start": 175,
      "line_end": 175
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ba_feng_han",
      "speaker_name": "跋锋寒",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "我第一次见到大河，是在陇西的黄河河段，其奔腾澎湃之势，有若自天上滚流而来，令我连呼吸都停顿了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 137,
      "line_start": 185,
      "line_end": 187
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dong_shu_ni",
      "speaker_name": "董淑妮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "追兵快来了！你们还在谈风说月的！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 137,
      "line_start": 195,
      "line_end": 197
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ba_feng_han",
      "speaker_name": "跋锋寒",
      "listener": "char_dong_shu_ni",
      "text": "小姐放心，太阳沉下西山后，我们便动程往偃师去，大家趁这机会休息一下，顺便欣赏大河落日的美景。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 137,
      "line_start": 199,
      "line_end": 201
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_dong_shu_ni",
      "text": "肚子饿吗？",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 137,
      "line_start": 209,
      "line_end": 211
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dong_shu_ni",
      "speaker_name": "董淑妮",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "终于有人来理淑妮了！我不是饿，而是饿得要命，有甚么可以吃的？",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 137,
      "line_start": 213,
      "line_end": 215
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_dong_shu_ni",
      "text": "老跋还有几片风干的免肉，是我亲手调味的，非常好吃，你要不要试试看？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 137,
      "line_start": 217,
      "line_end": 219
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_dong_shu_ni",
      "text": "你不是饿得要命吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 137,
      "line_start": 223,
      "line_end": 223
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dong_shu_ni",
      "speaker_name": "董淑妮",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "我不吃他的东西，他对人家很凶哩！",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 137,
      "line_start": 225,
      "line_end": 225
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_ba_feng_han",
      "text": "老跋！你在甚么地方开罪了人家董大小姐，累得她情愿饿着肚子也不吃你的东西？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 137,
      "line_start": 227,
      "line_end": 229
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ba_feng_han",
      "speaker_name": "跋锋寒",
      "listener": "char_dong_shu_ni",
      "text": "董小姐大人不记小人过，请赏脸！",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 137,
      "line_start": 231,
      "line_end": 233
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dong_shu_ni",
      "speaker_name": "董淑妮",
      "listener": "char_ba_feng_han",
      "text": "算你哩！这样子差不多。",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 137,
      "line_start": 235,
      "line_end": 237
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dong_shu_ni",
      "speaker_name": "董淑妮",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "你的手艺相当不错。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 137,
      "line_start": 245,
      "line_end": 247
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ba_feng_han",
      "speaker_name": "跋锋寒",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "我和子陵到高处看看，仲少你陪大小姐在这里好好歇息，待会还要赶路。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 137,
      "line_start": 249,
      "line_end": 251
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_dong_shu_ni",
      "text": "究竟是谁想害你大舅舅呢？是否越王和元文都？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 137,
      "line_start": 253,
      "line_end": 255
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dong_shu_ni",
      "speaker_name": "董淑妮",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "他们凭甚么来对付我大舅舅，当然是另有大后台在背后撑他们的腰哩！",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 137,
      "line_start": 257,
      "line_end": 259
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_dong_shu_ni",
      "text": "你不是说李密吧！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 137,
      "line_start": 261,
      "line_end": 261
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dong_shu_ni",
      "speaker_name": "董淑妮",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "你猜错了！但究竟是谁我只会告诉大舅舅，大舅舅便常教我要分清楚那些事可以对人说，那些事是不可对人说的。咦！太阳下山了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 137,
      "line_start": 263,
      "line_end": 265
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_dong_shu_ni",
      "text": "你不说我也知是谁，定是独孤家的人，对吧！啊！",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 137,
      "line_start": 269,
      "line_end": 271
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dong_shu_ni",
      "speaker_name": "董淑妮",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "你这人倒有点道行，难怪大舅舅那么注意你们的事，独孤家的人我没有一个欢喜的。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 137,
      "line_start": 273,
      "line_end": 275
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dong_shu_ni",
      "speaker_name": "董淑妮",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "尤其那个独孤峰，每次见到人家都从头看到脚，好像想用眼睛把人家的衣服脱掉似的，可厌之极。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 137,
      "line_start": 277,
      "line_end": 279
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_dong_shu_ni",
      "text": "洛阳现在的情况如何？是否已落进独孤家的手内哩？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 137,
      "line_start": 283,
      "line_end": 285
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dong_shu_ni",
      "speaker_name": "董淑妮",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "那轮得到他们，守城的郎奉叔叔和宋蒙秋叔叔都是大舅舅的心腹，只有皇宫的禁卫由独孤峰统辖，兵力不过五千，若非用阴谋手段，那是大舅舅的对手。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 137,
      "line_start": 287,
      "line_end": 289
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dong_shu_ni",
      "speaker_name": "董淑妮",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "和你说话很有趣！你这人很聪明，长得又好看。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 137,
      "line_start": 293,
      "line_end": 293
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_dong_shu_ni",
      "text": "你才是人间绝色，有倾国倾城的美貌，究竟你大舅舅将你许配了人家没有呢？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 137,
      "line_start": 295,
      "line_end": 297
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dong_shu_ni",
      "speaker_name": "董淑妮",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "人家今年才十七岁嘛，才不想那么快嫁人呢。嘻！你想不想娶我呢？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 137,
      "line_start": 299,
      "line_end": 301
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_dong_shu_ni",
      "text": "你不但长得美，还非常特别，我还是第一趟听到漂亮的女孩子问我这问题。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 137,
      "line_start": 303,
      "line_end": 305
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dong_shu_ni",
      "speaker_name": "董淑妮",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "说说不可以吗？又不是当真的。你们汉人的头脑真拘谨。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 137,
      "line_start": 307,
      "line_end": 309
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_dong_shu_ni",
      "text": "难道你不是汉人吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 137,
      "line_start": 311,
      "line_end": 311
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dong_shu_ni",
      "speaker_name": "董淑妮",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "谁告诉你我是汉人呢？人人都知大舅舅不是汉人，就只你不知道。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 137,
